{"tid":947134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"永別了《櫻桃小丸子》　完結篇聖誕節發行","createTime":"2018-12-19T04:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T12:08:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc72737d0b3e221606cda607e8e0c0f05528858","tid":947134,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"隨著日本國民漫畫家櫻桃子在8月乳癌離世，櫻桃子的名作《櫻桃小丸子》也成為絕響，出版商「集英社」宣布，將在12月25日聖誕節這天，發行《櫻桃小丸子》完結篇第17卷，為《櫻桃小丸子》畫下完美句點。<br />\n據日本《每日新聞》報導，在《櫻桃小丸子》完結卷中，並沒有櫻桃子的新作品，而是收錄過去未在單行本刊登的全7集漫畫，包括25周年紀念「神奇的魔法卡」特別版、電視動畫「小丸子弄丟存摺篇」，以及30周年紀念創作的「小丸子憧憬夏威夷篇」。<br />\n《櫻桃小丸子》從1986年在少女漫畫雜誌《Ribon》開始連載，之後成為日本國民漫畫，多年下來共賣了超過3200萬本，並被改成電視動漫，無論是大人還是小孩，《櫻桃小丸子》可謂當代最有人氣漫畫之一。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181219/640_a29e89c69c96d7309576cc37f3ce0e2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181219%2F640_a29e89c69c96d7309576cc37f3ce0e2b.jpg&h=6eb85592&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37fc7a3021a69bdae27e1791d000d18dc569257e","tid":947134,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"童年回憶<br />\n再見了小丸子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df13a9a1cc816abc583cc6480ac493b6eccb1505","tid":947134,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ec072f689156fb54e689fc1d2e7fd9bb03833f","tid":947134,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"回憶就是美.............<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f1ed8834c12fb9d22877899bd1c9f39b93ac1a","tid":947134,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67b8b317bd76360d45eda5234380785c3513f7b"